[YUKI]
You both have valid points.

00:20:13.963 --> 00:20:15.382 position:50% align:center
[KIMI]
If the guy flirts back,

00:20:15.465 --> 00:20:17.634 position:50% align:center
maybe that means he doesn't
love his girlfriend enough.

00:20:17.717 --> 00:20:20.387 position:50% align:center
[MANABE] At least some of the
responsibility is yours, too.

00:20:20.470 --> 00:20:22.263 position:50% align:center
[KIMI gasps]

00:20:22.347 --> 00:20:27.268 position:50% align:center
[YUKI] Still, if he can talk so
easily about loving somebody,

00:20:27.352 --> 00:20:29.604 position:50% align:center
I guess he can't be all bad.

00:20:32.982 --> 00:20:34.359 position:50% align:center
[YUKI]
And earlier,

00:20:34.442 --> 00:20:37.278 position:50% align:center
when I blurted out that stuff
about not being friends,

00:20:37.362 --> 00:20:40.573 position:50% align:center
I wasn't even thinking.

00:20:40.657 --> 00:20:46.037 position:50% align:center
But maybe that part of me
isn't so bad, either.

00:20:46.121 --> 00:20:50.166 position:50% align:center
I hope that when I look back
on the person I am now,

00:20:50.250 --> 00:20:53.420 position:50% align:center
seeing him will make me smile.

00:20:53.503 --> 00:20:57.340 position:50% align:center
I wonder if I'll ever
feel that way.

00:20:57.424 --> 00:21:03.471 position:50% align:center
[TOHRU] Don't worry.
You will. I'm sure of it.

00:21:05.473 --> 00:21:08.476 position:50% align:center
[YUKI] Here. I got you
a souvenir, Machi.

00:21:08.560 --> 00:21:11.396 position:50% align:center
They just came raining down.
It was beautiful.

00:21:11.479 --> 00:21:12.814 position:50% align:center
You want one, Nao?

00:21:12.897 --> 00:21:15.025 position:50% align:center
Why would I want a stupid leaf?

00:21:15.108 --> 00:21:17.027 position:50% align:center
Wow, ungrateful much?

00:21:17.110 --> 00:21:19.279 position:50% align:center
We came here as soon
as we got back, too.

00:21:19.362 --> 00:21:20.947 position:50% align:center
You really are a
jerk, shortstack.

00:21:21.031 --> 00:21:23.366 position:50% align:center
[NAOHITO]
I said I didn't want anything!

00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:27.454 position:50% align:center
[YUKI] They'll shine
softly... inside of you.

00:21:31.666 --> 00:21:32.917 position:50% align:center
[TOHRU groans]

00:21:33.001 --> 00:21:35.628 position:50% align:center
[TOHRU]
I tried my best, but still...

00:21:35.712 --> 00:21:38.798 position:50% align:center
...they came out
a little off somehow.

00:21:40.550 --> 00:21:42.594 position:50% align:center
Oh, well. At least
they're mostly done.

00:21:42.677 --> 00:21:43.595 position:50% align:center
[knocking]

00:21:43.678 --> 00:21:44.554 position:50% align:center
[KYO]
Tohru, got a sec?

00:21:44.637 --> 00:21:46.389 position:50% align:center
Uh! Sure!

00:21:46.473 --> 00:21:48.516 position:50% align:center
What's up, Kyo?
Is something wrong?

00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:52.103 position:50% align:center
[KYO] Nah, Shigure was asking
if you wanna eat out today.

00:21:52.187 --> 00:21:55.148 position:50% align:center
Wait, you haven't changed
out of your uniform yet?

00:21:55.231 --> 00:21:56.441 position:50% align:center
So tired you fell asleep?

00:21:56.524 --> 00:21:59.778 position:50% align:center
Oh, no. I just got
a little distracted.

00:21:59.861 --> 00:22:01.237 position:50% align:center
Distracted?

00:22:01.321 --> 00:22:05.158 position:50% align:center
Yeah, well, um, I wanted
to get them all finished.

00:22:05.241 --> 00:22:07.827 position:50% align:center
The zodiac figurines.

00:22:07.911 --> 00:22:11.373 position:50% align:center
I guess it's silly.
They're not very well made.

00:22:11.456 --> 00:22:14.042 position:50% align:center
And I haven't colored
them all yet.

00:22:15.794 --> 00:22:17.420 position:50% align:center
[KYO]
You idiot.

00:22:19.172 --> 00:22:22.634 position:50% align:center
[YUKI]
Add color and they will shine.

00:23:57.479 --> 00:23:59.230 position:50% align:center
[HATSUHARU]
"Do you wanna kiss?"